{"tid":1747004,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【致TVB廣告商，我哋俾機會你悔改！】每日洗版任務 - 紅底 \"雅芳婷\"","createTime":"2019-11-23T04:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T15:34:25.000Z","uid":267969,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"3e53a2dd6c7b3de9802d6594f1f2a7ebc06df3af","tid":1747004,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:20:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">致TVB廣告商，最後和解機會！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/75250837_496724671184387_502106815345983488_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ohc=8Rm6Pkot9F8AQn21FVvL4YeCWAPOugb7xpZWRQ0vdl7KV53SfbA4CH5iA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=dff1d26d34cbe2b5272c20996d0fd887&amp;oe=5E842D40\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F75250837_496724671184387_502106815345983488_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ohc%3D8Rm6Pkot9F8AQn21FVvL4YeCWAPOugb7xpZWRQ0vdl7KV53SfbA4CH5iA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Ddff1d26d34cbe2b5272c20996d0fd887%26oe%3D5E842D40&h=1131f97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/496724667851054/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fphotos%2Fa.417570699099785%2F496724667851054%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=8a35a137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/496724667851054/?type=3&amp;theater</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">抗爭要堅持，屌柒TVB成習慣<br />\n只需每日幾秒，救助被洗腦藍絲&amp;老豆老母</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】</span></strong><br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n5. tag 多幾個friend做任 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真，P牌每日只開一個抵制TVB行動post<br />\n唔會開9up post，<span style=\"color: red;\">請follow我個acc</span>、推post<br />\n<br />\n是日精選@23 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>雅芳婷</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://facebook.com/afontanehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fafontanehk%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=2c447a88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/afontanehk/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dpmhome/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdpmhome%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=17282f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dpmhome/</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※記得用留言template</strong></span></span><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/78259763_503959657127555_4575037268649050112_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ohc=HFqfpLnFmU4AQkNtRor-8_kB0M7j9r19BUcEfT1j0xirQaP13QndZYrgQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=95c47f01a973373cb19a77b952936aef&amp;oe=5E4BD615\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F78259763_503959657127555_4575037268649050112_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ohc%3DHFqfpLnFmU4AQkNtRor-8_kB0M7j9r19BUcEfT1j0xirQaP13QndZYrgQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D95c47f01a973373cb19a77b952936aef%26oe%3D5E4BD615&h=fc667bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>講下臭屎</strong></span><br />\n老細係紅底廠商會常務會董<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廠商會大力支持送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，支持克警嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要買床品，一定幫襯<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">停用TVB既Ecosa！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Source]<br />\n廠商會支持修例 - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33cdZXY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33cdZXY&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=7e251c6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33cdZXY</a><br />\n廠商會支持克警 - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33buqUB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33buqUB&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=7ada7587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33buqUB</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎用呢幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&h=ffeb70a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OFB5XW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OFB5XW.jpg&h=34f0d91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=52d9de24\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>  <br />\n －－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=2100bbeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb <br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=65785daf\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 抵制綜合組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=1284acbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb</a><br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=35036a3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a>"},{"pid":"ba580cd4daf2603caf8218a15bb96e43c980e334","tid":1747004,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"怒推"},{"pid":"f5fb82d4521904c7fd38de38ab0d9aacb5ade5ae","tid":1747004,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6b0dc32bef96774aed819654923e1b19d17c41","tid":1747004,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"7841cb8f63225b6fdf117f8d14508512c90b8fb1","tid":1747004,"uid":310858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"你估搭旅遊巴d公公婆婆知唔知自己犯緊法？？？？？<